Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8.0.0), cmake, kdelibs5-dev, libkscreen-dev (>= 1.0.1), libqjson-dev (>= 0.8), libxrandr-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.4
Homepage: https://projects.kde.org/projects/playground/base/kscreen
Vcs-Browser: http://bazaar.launchpad.net/~kubuntu-packagers/kubuntu-packaging/kscreen
